nhc_headline: ...TROPICAL STORM WATCHES AND WARNINGS ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF THE BAHAMAS...
summary: ...TROPICAL STORM WATCHES AND WARNINGS ISSUED FOR PORTIONS OF THE BAHAMAS... As of 5:00 PM EDT Fri Sep 26 the center of Nine was located near 20.9, -74.6 with movement NW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1008 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
